text: "Little Jeannie" is a 1980 song by Elton John and is taken from his 14th studio album 21 at 33. It went to number 1 in Canada, number 3 in the United States, number 4 in Switzerland, number 5 in New Zealand, number 8 in South Africa, number 9 in Australia and number 33 in the United States. == References == Category:1980 songs Category:Elton John songs Category:Soft rock songs
